                    <h1>Client Profile</h1>
                    <p>Search intent reveals what users truly want when they type queries into Google or an LLM.</p>
                    <p>It's the difference between someone asking "what is CRM software" and "Salesforce pricing demo"—and understanding this difference determines whether your content converts or just consumes budget.</p>
                    <p><span>Google's algorithms have evolved beyond keyword matching</span>. They now analyze user behavior patterns, click-through rates, and satisfaction signals to determine which results best serve each type of search intent. Intent-alignment is essential for rankings.</p>
